---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const whatsappGroupLink = "https://chat.whatsapp.com/Llt517pWQsrE8LP3CUayTI"; // Replace with your actual WhatsApp group link
---

<Layout hideNav={true}>
  <div class="thanks-container">
    <img src="/cover.png" alt="Background cover" class="background-image" />
    <div class="background-overlay"></div>

    <div class="hero-section">
      <h1 class="hero-title">¡Gracias por unirte!</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Has dado el primer paso hacia tu transformación. Te esperamos en el
        grupo de WhatsApp para continuar este viaje juntos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="thanks-content">
      <h2>¿Qué sigue?</h2>
      <p>
        En breve recibirás un correo electrónico con toda la información
        necesaria para comenzar tu viaje.
      </p>
      <p>
        Mientras tanto, únete a nuestro grupo de WhatsApp donde compartiremos
        contenido exclusivo y podrás conectar con otros seres conscientes que,
        como tú, han decidido dar el salto.
      </p>

      <div class="whatsapp-button-container">
        <a
          href={whatsappGroupLink}
          class="whatsapp-button"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <span>Unirse al Grupo de WhatsApp</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .thanks-container {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Fondo con gradiente y efecto de luz */
  .thanks-container::before {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom right,
      rgba(0, 13, 36, 0.5),
      rgba(0, 13, 36, 0.7),
      rgba(0, 13, 36, 0.9)
    );
    z-index: -2;
  }

  .thanks-container::after {
    content: "";
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle at center,
      rgba(0, 90, 255, 0.1),
      transparent,
      transparent
    );
    z-index: -1;
  }

  /* Imagen de fondo con efecto translúcido */
  .background-image {
    position: fixed;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    height: 100vh;
    width: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.35;
    mix-blend-mode: overlay;
    z-index: -3;
  }

  .background-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      rgba(0, 13, 36, 0.5),
      transparent,
      transparent
    );
    z-index: -2;
  }

  .hero-section {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #e2e8f0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .thanks-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .thanks-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .thanks-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .whatsapp-button-container {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .whatsapp-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background-color: #25d366;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .whatsapp-button:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .thanks-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .thanks-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .thanks-content p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
